    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在调查一份失踪人员报告后，你发现自己被困在地底深处。很快你就会发现，你并不孤单……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >被诅咒的恶魔无情追捕，你必须探索并逃离复杂的苏联时代地下掩体网络。制作工具帮助自己生存，明智地利用你有限的资源，而且<strong>不要被抓到</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091120/extras/5021f5ce2e57b721296ebabadac2b0a4.avif?t=1765376494\" width=600 height=70 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>探索</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >穿越苏联时代的掩体、隧道和下水道网络。发现神秘的仪式、奇怪的笔记，揭开这里发生的事情。是否还有其他人和你一同被困？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091120/extras/590833370cbb75c212f864f693c5597b.poster.avif?t=1765376494\" width=600 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091120/extras/590833370cbb75c212f864f693c5597b.webm?t=1765376494\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091120/extras/590833370cbb75c212f864f693c5597b.mp4?t=1765376494\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>搜寻</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >明智地使用你稀缺的资源，收集材料，制作工具来帮助你生存。以多种方式克服挑战，发现新工具，重新探索之前无法进入的掩体区域。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091120/extras/0c5c6f753ecc58c9bbf90c8d04f13ea8.poster.avif?t=1765376494\" width=600 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091120/extras/0c5c6f753ecc58c9bbf90c8d04f13ea8.webm?t=1765376494\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091120/extras/0c5c6f753ecc58c9bbf90c8d04f13ea8.mp4?t=1765376494\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>生存</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >要在致命的掩体网络中生存，你必须避免引起恶魔实体的注意。保持安静，躲在阴影中，当别无选择时，正面战斗或拼命逃跑。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091120/extras/ef3797658ead32f2eff0fd66db9451ec.poster.avif?t=1765376494\" width=600 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091120/extras/ef3797658ead32f2eff0fd66db9451ec.webm?t=1765376494\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091120/extras/ef3797658ead32f2eff0fd66db9451ec.mp4?t=1765376494\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>主要特色：</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >避开一个对你的行动作出反应并无情追捕你的智能怪物</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索并逃离复杂的掩体、隧道和下水道网络</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >制作临时工具，管理你有限的资源以生存</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与世界和其中的生物进行高保真互动</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >揭开恶魔实体的起源和他们力量的源泉</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >程序化生成确保每次游戏体验都独一无二</p></li></ul>",
